                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9592" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0321</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">915 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食泽民众，业润社会：白象食品的企业社会责任担当</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Feeding the People, Enriching Society: Baixiang Food’s Commitment to Corporate Social Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨帆，宋颜殊，陆秀军，张正勇，刘军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">白象食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">白象食品；企业社会责任；利益相关者；企业社会责任履责新范式；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Baixiang Food; Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR); Stakeholders; New Paradigms of Corporate Social Responsibility Fulfillment; Strategic Corporate Social Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">白象食品作为中国知名食品制造企业，始终坚持“食泽民众，业润社会”的理念，在保证产品质量与产品创新的同时，助力乡村振兴，开展教育帮扶，关爱残障员工，注重环境保护，积极参与各类公益活动，展现了良好的企业形象。本案例通过描写白象食品全面履行社会责任的具体实践以及白象食品在社会责任实践中形成的特色与经验，旨在使学生掌握企业社会责任的内涵、企业社会责任的类型、利益相关者理论、企业社会责任履责新范式、战略性企业社会责任的教学内容，使学生能够判断企业履行的社会责任类型，掌握在常态和社会风险下开展企业社会责任实践的能力，启发学生思考战略性企业社会责任与企业可持续发展间的关系。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a renowned food manufacturing enterprise in China, Baixiang Food consistently adheres to the philosophy of “Benefiting the People through Food, Enriching Society through Industry”. While ensuring product quality and innovation, the company actively contributes to rural revitalization, conducts educational assistance programs, cares for employees with disabilities, emphasizes environmental protection, and actively participates in various public welfare activities, demonstrating a favorable corporate image. This case study, through depicting the specific practices of Baixiang Food in comprehensively fulfilling its social responsibilities as well as its unique features and experiences in this process, aims to enable students to grasp the essence of corporate social responsibility (CSR), understand the types of CSR, stakeholder theory, new paradigms of CSR fulfillment, and strategic CSR. It also seeks to empower students to identify the types of social responsibilities undertaken by enterprises, cultivate their ability to practice CSR in both normal and socially risky situations, and inspire them to reflect on the relationship between strategic CSR and corporate sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；利益相关者理论；企业社会责任履责新范式；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
